title: 01/23/2013 - The Church Of What's Happening Now #49
description:
Recorded live at Nerdist studios, so the sound is a little different. Joey's old friends Jody Ferdig and Dante join us in studio. Joey;s other friend Carlos from North Bergen calls up to talk about being a father.
